{"tid":2492824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【香港傳媒界都係一鳩樣】CNN被爆自認利用市民對武肺恐懼控制民心輿論走向提高收視幫手推防疫政策，香港有邊間傳媒有報？？","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T15:38:44.000Z","uid":88743,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4e2be8d1c7bfbd829728030da65aa41d323add","tid":2492824,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"專登係右邊大字寫死亡人數<br />\n每日都要提你呢啲數字<br />\n驚你唔記得左「疫情係好撚恐佈」呢回事<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPhRnAdPkgLhnKCu5ut6EjoSuRpkC95XHvxXCTqjXEvZP?filename=6wjaVoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wjaVoM.jpg&h=175a63d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVYykjJy7pWYER53Lw2aEW2QsqiuTw17wW6fQjkNMXcdG?filename=XwQmhB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwQmhB6.jpg&h=cb03e30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUhpDicf6xjmLwctBgLh5QxaAKADCxYEaJj8VEz5rFuoZ?filename=SDu2Mvr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDu2Mvr.jpg&h=b9870538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeUcTwkdvVrpgGYLxmad9AtU8NeryCbC11NiDeW1N95JQ?filename=G75YjQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG75YjQr.jpg&h=c920f74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbAPy2HpPn7Sp2UFkBRePYsTHYNYYJsfq21836FWnT3Fc?filename=Z24qKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ24qKg6.jpg&h=f2de3732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3jQfUm9a86NSqPsJbDHS4cUK1EVJvRh8qX1ypnWYN6D?filename=CZ9qKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZ9qKg6.jpg&h=f065fcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXfcupx3uJDfzEo6s6GBWxi5DdHLksdbjsWT9MwdYXrHV?filename=UOvYjQs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOvYjQs.jpg&h=255cc5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQAYvJQAaYyDemibMppTVffZiKhQJAxWXGrTHHWGvx8Hq?filename=aPS4foM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPS4foM.jpg&h=730bb0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIf it bleeds, it leads<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越死得人多，收視越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死得人多，就可以make our point better (我地講既野越有說服力)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要講左佢地點解唔報康復人數<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">因為康復人數唔會令到你地驚</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZdP5MnzbpjYx4GRzHmSpKqE7xHRy47Ksm4dwJKqxMVTY?filename=j5y7daM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5y7daM.jpg&h=883cbc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcs3jx8gW1b2HVaaBVC6ko6HaEr8B28ykokodzte1Q5V4?filename=wbQYjQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbQYjQM.jpg&h=01ea213a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3EirM3pbKDJFkYU5mXaYX8RV1HqoSXjXGEAMNzDuiym?filename=WxOGhDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxOGhDu.jpg&h=eff5d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9faQkIA6YNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9faQkIA6YNU&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=9f175ada\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9faQkIA6YNU</a><br />\n<br />\n報完之後人地成個Twitter account又俾人BAN鳩埋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma78vZTk7TQmhmDPncK99RxJanDUucxc5w3vSbdYqVLAG?filename=20pRETa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20pRETa.jpg&h=578b4044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵個仔都有retweet呢單野<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme8fDj5Yk7Xpa9vjbCNvwg6xVZxuxe1n4B7eyPUgHt3HP?filename=mLd3v23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLd3v23.jpg&h=23a05085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">香港以我所知好似得大紀元同白兵有報</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大紀元<br />\n【獨家】佛州州長：封鎖防疫是個巨大錯誤<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/4/16/n12885668.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F4%2F16%2Fn12885668.htm&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c3a3983c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/4/16/n12885668.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n白兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CVj9PwlRIAA?t=3997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCVj9PwlRIAA%3Ft%3D3997&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=107cb36e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CVj9PwlRIAA?t=3997</a><br />\n１：０６：37<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">香港懶人包就都有提過下CNN偷拍呢單野，但係佢只係有講有關CNN承認點樣整死TRUMP果PART，無講CNN用武肺推高收視恐嚇觀眾果PART</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">【簡單黎講即係即係香港懶人包專登唔提】</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtGAxXf7mXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRtGAxXf7mXw&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=2b6854e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtGAxXf7mXw</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">其他傳媒自媒有無報？？？<br />\n<br />\n老蕭有無報？<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n琴日片段截圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfJotXdozGf4ja5edFP2PqotmZUofiS1H16vvKt3gtcaM?filename=9qPRERW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qPRERW.jpg&h=5021cb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmm7mxPyhUc4TPKDRpo98pTdGv4YwEk8dS6fZ4VQRcsW?filename=uorkybV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuorkybV.jpg&h=42f595bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVxTpDgiMKTTYggbtzFRxYg7MbZ2GkWSHm9a5m1qDaYBh?filename=2Ks4fqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ks4fqf.jpg&h=a3807bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">蘋果有無報？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmakf8PxkTc61tKKPLNKizEEAxXcqvmHJY6DhgubxdKWfv?filename=p5sWQYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5sWQYT.png&h=83002d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果同你講，你應該要「驚到震」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道其他香港傳媒自媒有報呢單野既唔該留個言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3217203d00f269ff16f928c0faf3c141d5419e","tid":2492824,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"老燒一日浪費好撚多A4紙同油墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d85faffe3c5175696e3b38bd9fa71501f339a4a","tid":2492824,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3217203d00f269ff16f928c0faf3c141d5419e","tid":2492824,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"老燒一日浪費好撚多A4紙同油墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"日日係度報武肺幾多人中<br />\n<br />\n有少少無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a7525c212c43c5d5b16be8462312b063f5fb60","tid":2492824,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike